tps://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180309%2Fs00002%2F1520531843099&d=aQe3t%2B%2BtQzHLQ0HOokJk7ZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=59ae97ec\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180309%2Fs00002%2F1520531843099&h=61222b1d\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20180309/s00002/1520531843099</a><br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】政府推動全民閱讀，中央圖書館4月22日會搞一場破格嘅同樂日，配合4月23號嘅「世界閱讀日」。<span style=\"color: red;\">圖書館總館長（香港中央圖書館及推廣活動）鄭劉美莉</span>喺康文署嘅傳媒茶敘上同Emily透露咗當日有咩活動，佢話圖書館環境好靜，唔畀影相，不過同樂日就唔同喇，中圖將有現場音樂演奏，例如爵士樂，仲有時段畀市民點唱𠻹。"},{"pid":"632280c7cff1177b737f24c6bb5ee259980bf535","tid":637824,"uid":15739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc12befc60c11ced0cd36a2b506366b451ce8654","tid":637824,"uid":15625,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T06:26:35.000Z","msg":"打上1823投訴啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20180309/s00002/1520531843099\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180309%2Fs00002%2F1520531843099&d=aQe3t%2B%2BtQzHLQ0HOokJk7ZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=59ae97ec\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180309%2Fs00002%2F1520531843099&h=61222b1d\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20180309/s00002/1520531843099</a><br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】政府推動全民閱讀，中央圖書館4月22日會搞一場破格嘅同樂日，配合4月23號嘅「世界閱讀日」。<span style=\"color: red;\">圖書館總館長（香港中央圖書館及推廣活動）鄭劉美莉</span>喺康文署嘅傳媒茶敘上同Emily透露咗當日有咩活動，佢話圖書館環境好靜，唔畀影相，不過同樂日就唔同喇，中圖將有現場音樂演奏，例如爵士樂，仲有時段畀市民點唱𠻹。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T06:43:16.000Z","msg":"個館長應該比錢買翻黎"},{"pid":"ca18d27e6fe9c41ecf1362807991cfd3e6f8047f","tid":637824,"uid":142824,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"quote":{"pid":"601e8b298a48155422b3113072ec4c0cbd991c7b","tid":637824,"uid":148983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T06:18:22.000Z","msg":"邊個撚屌批埋啲咁嘅活動係圖書館搞咖 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T06:46:46.000Z","msg":"去過中央圖書館都知所有樓層都係通嘅，你響裡面玩音樂，唔使諗都知啲回音大到清潔阿嬸都高潮，如果唔係點解圖書館裡面無BGM（好似無）<br />\n<br />\n佢地個腦唔係裝豆腐花嘅話，其實都好難解釋點解會諗到啲濕勁嘅野。<br />\n<br />\n最好笑嘅係圖書館出面明明有空地，結果同佢地個腦一樣要人開聲屌先肯用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f4f0b1f8b83c5af6f5390967b4a0752a9bcf1f4","tid":637824,"uid":28309,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T07:02:07.000Z","msg":"成個政府都用屎忽諗野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n免費dse之後就圖書館演奏會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3304322568f8cce8fb38994a60391bd4f761b969","tid":637824,"uid":15935,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T07:19:11.000Z","msg":"其實香港啲圖書館真係好撚廢，藏書量少唔在講，一個地區分館藏書一定少撚過大學ulib<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n乜柒文化活動都無得做，呢個問題係因為設計個陣嘅短視啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 圖書館真係只係用嚟睇書咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有套記錄片講紐約圖書館，人地嘅圖書館簡直就係凝聚社區嘅地標<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 香港嘅呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一個地方可以做晒各式各樣嘅分享會(音樂演奏/作者新書發佈乜乜柒柒/學術論壇)、文化同知識傳承活動(幫啲低下階層勞工增值+解決社區/種族問題+幫佢地啲細路擴闊眼界)，就算漫無目的咁入去hea都十分之寫意。人地主館同分館又有唔同嘅服務對象同角色定位，任何年齡層都起碼會覺得圖書館係一座有價值嘅建築物，就算入去鳩行可能都會有啲得著。<br />\n香港圖書館，你問下自己幾耐無入過去借過啲out撚晒date嘅書？仲要乜柒都無得搞。根本就on撚99食賓周<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92b6a44f1303d002eb923ca9c36a644f3c258699","tid":637824,"uid":169663,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e0a54a3b8f093c84c07be6ec1c40a7f2f7e5a289","tid":637824,"uid":54472,"like":86,"dislike":0,"score":86,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T07:50:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DHhy2Gk_xik\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DDHhy2Gk_xik&d=aQe3t%2B%2BtQzHLQ0HOokJk7ZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=848f0187\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DHhy2Gk_xik</a> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T07:32:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=riWMkYD1uN4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DriWMkYD1uN4&d=aQe3t%2B%2BtQzHLQ0HOokJk7ZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=c6a80595\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=riWMkYD1uN4</a>"},{"pid":"2f433aee1aa227324a0e37fa40b4befa1a108e1c","tid":637824,"uid":33053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T07:42:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0a2db7934ddcffdb935f2f0aeec585d6dcc8ce5","tid":637824,"uid":33441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T09:08:53.000Z","msg":"等開concert <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a84fa6c536be4b35db173885c107c5792335978","tid":637824,"uid":115888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T10:46:56.000Z","msg":"笑左"},{"pid":"fc43e15f045e82997eae09470c385257ffa78d60","tid":637824,"uid":88029,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T11:01:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c5bd215df3a1936c32cb080e4b9ccf58bbf6f4dd","tid":637824,"uid":88366,"like":